data.description:
Welcome to your dream home in the heart of Central Fort Walton Beach! This delightful residence boasts a classic white-washed brick exterior, complemented by a durable metal roof, offering timeless curb appeal. Located just 4.1 miles from the pristine sandy white beaches, and surrounded by convenient shopping and delectable restaurants, this property epitomizes both comfort and convenience.Step inside to discover a spacious interior adorned with beautiful 12 mm laminate floors throughout and tasteful tile in the bathrooms. The expansive open kitchen is a chef's delight, featuring a large kitchen island and elegant granite countertops, creating the perfect space for culinary creativity and social gatherings.Upgrades abound in this meticulously maintained home, including a newer HVAC air handler and condenser, as well as double-paned windows that infuse the space with natural light. The electrical system has been thoughtfully rewired with all copper wiring, accompanied by a newer panel, outlets, and switches, ensuring both safety and efficiency.

Enjoy the serenity of your expansive backyard with a privacy fence, offering the perfect setting for outdoor activities and relaxation. The front yard is equally impressive, featuring newer irrigation, a lawn pump, and timer.

This residence is not just a home; it's a lifestyle. Embrace the comfort, style, and convenience that this Central Fort Walton Beach gem has to offer. Schedule your viewing today and make this charming property your new home sweet home!

To view this property virtually copy and paste the link into your browser: https://my.matterport.com/show/?m=ZjJoAHRDDPh&mls=1
